<subSubSection id="4FFD6520FFBDFFEBD0ECFC257A85FBB9" pageId="3" pageNumber="26" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="075836ABFFBDFFEBD0ECFC257A85FBB9" blockId="3.[151,1437,450,1053]" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis id="3593EAB9FFBDFFEBD0ECFC257933FC71" bold="true" box="[199,315,955,981]" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">Remarks.</emphasis>
We checked the male specimen (MIZPAS) from 
<collectingCountry id="7FF0763BFFBDFFEBD356FC257BC4FC71" box="[893,972,955,981]" name="Vietnam" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">Tonkin</collectingCountry>
identified as 
<taxonomicName id="C0E74D28FFBDFFEBD445FC227D06FC71" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1851" box="[1134,1294,955,981]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Penthimia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fulviventris">
<emphasis id="3593EAB9FFBDFFEBD445FC227D06FC71" box="[1134,1294,955,981]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">B. fulviventris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Schmidt (
<bibRefCitation id="63764B5AFFBDFFEBD0B4FC417959FC5D" author="Schmidt, E." box="[159,337,991,1017]" pageId="3" pageNumber="26" pagination="116 - 120" refId="ref9039" refString="Schmidt, E. (1920 a) Beitrage Zur Kenntnis aussereuropaischer Zikaden (Rhynchota, Homoptera) XIV Zur Kenntnis der Tribus Sudrini. Archiv fur Naturgeschichte, 85, 116 - 120." type="journal article" year="1920">Schmidt, 1920a</bibRefCitation>
) but it should be 
<taxonomicName id="C0E74D28FFBDFFEBD23DFC7E7A5CFC5D" authorityName="Shen &amp; Zhang" authorityYear="1995" box="[534,596,991,1017]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Balala" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lui">
<emphasis id="3593EAB9FFBDFFEBD23DFC7E7A5CFC5D" box="[534,596,991,1017]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">B. lui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
according to the genitalia. So we delete the distributional record in 
<collectingCountry id="7FF0763BFFBDFFEBD566FC417D94FC5D" box="[1357,1436,991,1017]" name="Vietnam" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">Tonkin</collectingCountry>
from 
<taxonomicName id="C0E74D28FFBDFFEBD0FEFB9A797AFBB9" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1851" box="[213,370,1027,1053]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Penthimia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fulviventris">
<emphasis id="3593EAB9FFBDFFEBD0FEFB9A797AFBB9" box="[213,370,1027,1053]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">B. fulviventris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and add 
<collectingCountry id="7FF0763BFFBDFFEBD1FCFB9D7A2EFBB9" box="[471,550,1027,1053]" name="Vietnam" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">Tonkin</collectingCountry>
to 
<taxonomicName id="C0E74D28FFBDFFEBD261FB9A7A8FFBB9" authorityName="Shen &amp; Zhang" authorityYear="1995" box="[586,647,1027,1053]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Balala" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lui">
<emphasis id="3593EAB9FFBDFFEBD261FB9A7A8FFBB9" box="[586,647,1027,1053]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="26">B. lui</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
